isis.stitle: TSI 98-12-09 - New Engine Control Module (ECM) in Service Parts for the International® DT 466E and 530E Engines with ECM 3-Box System Mounted on Cab Cowl

subjectgroup.subject: New Engine Control Module (ECM) in Service Parts for the International® DT 466E and 530E Engines with ECM 3-Box System Mounted on Cab Cowl

geninfo.para: This service letter is for vehicles with the International® DT 466E and 530E engines and with the ECM (known as the 3-Box Electronic Control system) mounted to the cab cowl.

note.para: Current production for all vehicles with these engines are being built with the ECM (single controller) mounted to the engine.

geninfo.para: A new ECM is released for service for the 3-Box System. The new service part ECM offers the latest software and updated calibrations. Also to improve parts ordering, new service part numbers are reduced to (6), see the following tables.

table.title: DT 466E High Torque (HT) With Non-Split Shot Fuel Injectors
DT 466E Standard Torque (ST) With Non-Split Shot Fuel Injectors
DT 466E High Torque (HT) With Split Shot Fuel Injectors
DT 466E Standard Torque (ST) With Split Shot Fuel Injectors
